  <div class="ex-details">
    <h2>Advanced Fertility Treatments</h2>
    <p>Our state-of-the-art embryology lab is equipped with time-lapse imaging, blastocyst culture systems, and vitrification facilities &mdash; ensuring the highest possible pregnancy rates per cycle. Each couple receives a fully personalised protocol after detailed diagnostic workup.</p>
    <p>We are committed to transparency: honest success rates, clear pricing, and compassionate counselling at every step. There are no hidden charges, no false promises &mdash; just evidence-based medicine delivered with warmth.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Basic & advanced IVF cycles</li>
      <li>ICSI & PICSI</li>
      <li>Donor egg & donor sperm programmes</li>
      <li>Surrogacy counselling</li>
      <li>Laser-assisted hatching</li>
      <li>Blastocyst transfer</li>
      <li>Semen analysis & andrology</li>
      <li>Recurrent miscarriage workup</li>
    </ul>
